{"tid":1392113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我以電筒收藏家既身份話比連登仔聽！","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T10:59:44.000Z","uid":281029,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"515f48ef48ecdcd6a1ab803c9efa36ead1deca63","tid":1392113,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"近排實在收到太多email，<br />\n問我呢支電筒得唔得，果支好唔好。<br />\n如果講電筒理論既話，會好複雜，大家一定唔會睇。<br />\n所以我以世界遠射最強，最貼近最近實際應用場合，同埋最經濟，<br />\n呢幾個因素，只推薦以下一支電筒。<br />\n<br />\nLumintop BLF GT<br />\n已經出左唔同版本，記住係XHP35HI版本。遠射2公里！<br />\n<br />\n呢支電筒，雖然強國代工，但筒身，軟件，<br />\n都係美國BLF電筒論壇（<a href=\"http://budgetlightforum.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbudgetlightforum.com%2F&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=de1118ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://budgetlightforum.com/</a>）班痴線發燒友設計。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">佢地設計呢支電筒，並非為實用，純碎為遠射而遠射。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nEbay或者淘寶都可以買到，價錢大約2000蚊樓下。<br />\n<br />\n記住，遠射，唔可以睇流明（有幾光），而要睇光線集中度，呢個同LED核心設計、反光杯設計好大關係。但同時要注意，唔好射到人，太集中既光線，輕則短暫失明，重則視力永久受損。"},{"pid":"b346f17a062efe4c55c7fdec19e295e5d5979001","tid":1392113,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"射到眼好大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a033ca54da953004a59b6584f516902738e2945","tid":1392113,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月3日 旺角遊行<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"ad8ae05d364df49004f145893ac54f1c3bb20edd","tid":1392113,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:54:22.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abDpOOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abDpOOU</a><br />\n<br />\